Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A long winter is coming to the Land of Wano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki, I want you to use your power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I die."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kozuki Toki and Kozuki Oden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They left the Land of Wano\Nto the new generation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and fell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Back to the Present Day!\N20 Years Later!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold! It's cold! It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to boil the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already boiling, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold, it's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}, it's already scalding hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel cold! I can't stop shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me the Kozuki samurai retainers' bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you find them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the proof of their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast nine shadows on the \Nnight woven of 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you shall know the \Nbrilliance of the dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a long way to go\Nuntil this country sees its dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"20 years"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa, kappappa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa and pa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa, kappappa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa and pa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! This is the Kappa Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa, kappappa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappappa and pa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you! You're filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really live here in the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're quite strong!\N--Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,KYOSHIRO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... So you guys are \Nthe Kyoshiro Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your head up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to serve as my guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be an honor, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm! Good, good! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a \Nlittle something for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make you happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this, money, ladies, soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can provide everything you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice! Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel extremely honored, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Too good to be true! Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How resourceful! And he can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a yakuza\Nwho's taking the place of Boss Hyogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyoshiro Family dominates \Nthe Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a weakness, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he always looks tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So people call him Napping Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably too much nightlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ushimitsu Kozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole money from the storehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,USHIMITSU KOZO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a cute girl here in the doorway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be an orphan \Nslipped into the capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor thing is starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiyori-{\i0}sama{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be hard to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I am identifying \Nmyself as Kyoshiro now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am actually one of the Akazaya Nine,\NOden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s retainers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Denjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Denjiro?! You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is true. Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see you again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu helped me escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had stayed with him,\Nhe would've given me all his food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wouldn't have eaten at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He would've died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}, look at me closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My face is haunted by a ghost called wrath...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...so much so even Kin'emon and the others\Nwould not recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is what we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the moment the great \Nbattle begins someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,do not tell anyone, even \Nour allies, about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of Kawamatsu,\NI will protect you from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell others that your name is Komurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushimitsu-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got money again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make sure to distribute \Nit in Ebisu Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. As I told you many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,carry fake blood under your kimono every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi is fixated on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,without knowing that you \Nare Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be tough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In case of an emergency,\NI will tear Orochi away from "Komurasaki" with "death."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make the people of the Flower Capital\Nbelieve that Komurasaki is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been almost 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now it's almost present day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few months before Luffy's raid\Non the night of the Fire Festival...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:52.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,A FEW MONTHS BEFORE THE FIRE FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghosts are really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So Toki's power was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon, Kanjuro, Raizo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikunojo, and Momonosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Five of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They came jumping from that day 20 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really such a power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,From that burning castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't someone playing a joke\Nto freak you out more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on the sea coast!\NSomeone will try to leave the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill them if they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After 20 years,\Nthere's something I wanna ask the remnants of the Kozuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, your spy is quite competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, he's a trustworthy man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was born and raised in a theater troupe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as a result of persecution in the Land of Wano,\Nhe lost his parents while they were on stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the family of the Daimyo killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah! Yeah!\N--They deserved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By playing characters,\Nhe survived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE A DESCENDANT OF\NTHE KUROZUMI CLAN'S MAIN FAMILY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NI killed those who slayed your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But our revenge is just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Live your life as a real Kozuki retainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and die as a Kozuki retainer\Nwithout letting anyone know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the important role\Nthat you've been given in this big play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR A PLACE TO DIE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,IT'S AN HONOR
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His only pleasure is to play someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I went to Oden Castle\Nto borrow money,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he brought out\Ntwice as much money as I asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ally with you\Nbecause I had that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the information about\Nthe silly lord Oden's raid was helpful for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...that he was really ready to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...with Oden and the others\Nin the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no mind of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I stop him,\Nhe'll live as a real Kozuki retainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and matter-of-factly send information...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...in an eerily loyal manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,FLOWER CAPITAL, PRESENT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well then, the legendary samurai\Nhas passed down to posterity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been 20 years since \NKozuki Oden's tragic death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the story of the two opposing clans,\Nthe Kozuki and the Kurozumi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the pirate, Kaido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To fulfill Kozuki Oden's dream of\Nopening up the borders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the samurai retainers\Njumped 20 years into the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,GRAVE OF KOZUKI ODEN\NGRAVE OF KOZUKI MOMONOSUKE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time passed and it's present day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three samurai and a ninja\Nsuccessfully traveled through time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With them is Oden's son\Nand the future Shogun of the Land of Wano, Momonosuke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must head for\NZou the Phantom Island whose location is a mystery!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their ship was wrecked when they almost reached Zou\Nand they were separated from Raizo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Later in Dressrosa, Momonosuke\Ngot on board a mysterious ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kin'emon pursued the ship,\Nseparating from Kanjuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Kin'emon arrived at...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the island of fire and ice, Punk Hazard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm finally separated from it-{\i1}bu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower body just talked!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kin'emon finally met...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momonosuke happened to eat the artificial Devil Fruit,\Nwhich enables him to transform into a dragon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and soon after met Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Kin'emon and Momonosuke reunited,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and headed for Dressrosa with Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Dressrosa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...their samurai colleague, Kanjuro,\Nwas waiting for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A deadly battle against a tough enemy,\NDonquixote Doflamingo, who ruled Dressrosa ensued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After taking down the Doflamingo Family,\Nthe group left Dressrosa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, they finally got to their true destination,\NZou the Phantom Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, they met Cat Viper and Dogstorm\Nwho lived in Kuri when they were young!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,People from the country of Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a retainer of the Kozuki Clan from the Land of Wano,\Nnamed Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to look for my comrade named Raizo\Nwho is a warrior from the same country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he been here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Raizo-{\i1}dono{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They reunited with Raizo\Nwho was protected by the Minks from Kaido's subordinates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's join hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have Kaido's head though!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the Ninja-Pirate-Mink-Samurai Alliance\Nwas formed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For months, they risked their lives\Nto recruit allies who'd fight with them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their persistence must've paid off\Nbecause 4,200 people stood up to fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weapons and ships are ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plenty of troops for the \Nraid are gathering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...at twilight today, the day of the Fire Festival,\Nat Tokage Port.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Head for Onigashima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be taken down by us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kin'emon decides to advance \Nbut faces challenges!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their retreat intercepted by Kaido's army,\Nthe Akazaya members are driven to a corner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats are nowhere to be found!\NBetrayal and despair! Wavering bonds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will the turbulent opening\Ninstantly bring the curtain down?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Sea Is For Pirates! Raid! To Onigashima!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:49.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,
